<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Deleted</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: #333; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px;">
    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-weight: 600;">Your account has been deleted</h2>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0;">Hi {{name}},</p>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0;">Your Examforge account and all associated personal data have been permanently deleted as requested.</p>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0;">The following data has been removed:</p>

    <ul style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #555;">
      <li>Your name, email address, and profile information</li>
      <li>Your login credentials and authentication data</li>
      <li>Your profile content and uploaded files</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">As required by law, certain financial transaction records (dates, amounts, transaction IDs) may be retained for up to 7 years for tax and audit purposes. These records are no longer linked to your identity.</p>

    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">Thank you for using Examforge. If you have any questions, please contact us at privacy@Examforge.com.</p>
  </body>
</html>
